    "engine": "knitr",
    "markdown": "---\ntitle: \"13. Conditional DPmixGPD with Stick-Breaking Backend\"\noutput:\n  rmarkdown::html_vignette:\n    highlight: null\n    code_folding: show\nvignette: >\n  %\\VignetteIndexEntry{13. Conditional DPmixGPD with Stick-Breaking Backend}\n  %\\VignetteEngine{knitr::rmarkdown}\n  %\\VignetteEncoding{UTF-8}\n---\n\n\n\n\n> **Legacy vignette (for the website / historical notes).**\n> These files may not match the current exported API one-to-one.\n> Last verified: **2026-01-18**.\n>\n> For the up-to-date workflow, see the main package vignettes (Introduction, Model Spec, MCMC Workflow, Unconditional/Conditional/Causal, Backends, S3 Reference).\n\n\n# Conditional DPmixGPD: Stick-Breaking Backend\n\n**Purpose**: Apply fixed-component stick-breaking truncation to covariate-dependent mixtures while keeping the GPD tail. This vignette mirrors `v10` but with the SB backend.\n\n---\n\n## Data Setup\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n```{.r .cell-code}\ndata(\"nc_posX100_p5_k4\")\ny <- nc_posX100_p5_k4$y\nX <- as.matrix(nc_posX100_p5_k4$X)\nif (is.null(colnames(X))) {\n  colnames(X) <- paste0(\"x\", seq_len(ncol(X)))\n}\n\nsummary_tbl <- tibble(\n  statistic = c(\"N\", \"Mean\", \"SD\", \"Min\", \"Max\"),\n  value = c(length(y), mean(y), sd(y), min(y), max(y))\n)\n\nggplot(data.frame(y = y, x1 = X[, 1]), aes(x = x1, y = y)) +\n  geom_point(alpha = 0.6, color = \"purple\") +\n  geom_smooth(method = \"loess\", color = \"orange\", fill = NA) +\n  labs(title = \"Tail Outcome vs x1 (SB)\", x = \"x1\", y = \"y\") +\n  theme_minimal()\n```\n\n::: {.cell-output-display}\n![](v13-conditional-DPmixGPD-SB_files/figure-html/data-setup-1.png){width=768}\n:::\n:::\n\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n::: {.cell-output-display}\n`````{=html}\n<table class=\"table table-striped table-hover\" style=\"width: auto !important; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\">\n<caption>Conditional Tail Summary (SB)</caption>\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th style=\"text-align:center;\"> statistic </th>\n   <th style=\"text-align:center;\"> value </th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n<tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td style=\"text-align:center;\"> N </td>\n   <td style=\"text-align:center;\"> 100.000 </td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td style=\"text-align:center;\"> Mean </td>\n   <td style=\"text-align:center;\"> 1.942 </td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td style=\"text-align:center;\"> SD </td>\n   <td style=\"text-align:center;\"> 1.146 </td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td style=\"text-align:center;\"> Min </td>\n   <td style=\"text-align:center;\"> 0.488 </td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td style=\"text-align:center;\"> Max </td>\n   <td style=\"text-align:center;\"> 5.278 </td>\n  </tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n\n`````\n:::\n:::\n\n\n---\n\n## Threshold\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n```{.r .cell-code}\nu_threshold <- quantile(y, 0.85)\n\nggplot(data.frame(y = y), aes(x = y)) +\n  geom_histogram(aes(y = after_stat(density)), bins = 40, fill = \"lightgreen\", alpha = 0.6, color = \"black\") +\n  geom_vline(xintercept = u_threshold, linetype = \"dashed\", color = \"black\") +\n  labs(title = \"Threshold for SB tail (85%)\", x = \"y\", y = \"Density\") +\n  theme_minimal()\n```\n\n::: {.cell-output-display}\n![](v13-conditional-DPmixGPD-SB_files/figure-html/threshold-1.png){width=768}\n:::\n:::\n\n\n---\n\n## Model Specification\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n```{.r .cell-code}\nbundle_sb_cond_gpd_gamma <- build_nimble_bundle(\n  y = y,\n  X = X,\n  kernel = \"gamma\",\n  backend = \"sb\",\n  GPD = TRUE,\n  components = 5,\n  param_specs = list(\n    gpd = list(\n      threshold = list(mode = \"link\", link = \"exp\")\n    )\n  ),\n  mcmc = mcmc\n)\n\nbundle_sb_cond_gpd_laplace <- build_nimble_bundle(\n  y = y,\n  X = X,\n  kernel = \"laplace\",\n  backend = \"sb\",\n  GPD = TRUE,\n  components = 5,\n  param_specs = list(\n    gpd = list(\n      threshold = list(mode = \"link\", link = \"exp\")\n    )\n  ),\n  mcmc = mcmc\n)\n```\n:::\n\n\n---\n\n## MCMC Execution\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n```{.r .cell-code}\nfit_sb_cond_gpd_gamma <- load_or_fit(\"v13-conditional-DPmixGPD-SB-fit_sb_cond_gpd_gamma\", run_mcmc_bundle_manual(bundle_sb_cond_gpd_gamma))\nfit_sb_cond_gpd_laplace <- load_or_fit(\"v13-conditional-DPmixGPD-SB-fit_sb_cond_gpd_laplace\", run_mcmc_bundle_manual(bundle_sb_cond_gpd_laplace))\nsummary(fit_sb_cond_gpd_gamma)\n```\n\n::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout}\n\n```\nMixGPD summary | backend: Stick-Breaking Process | kernel: Gamma Distribution | GPD tail: TRUE | epsilon: 0.025\nn = 100 | components = 5\nSummary\nInitial components: 5 | Components after truncation: 1\n\nWAIC: 300.892\nlppd: -132.126 | pWAIC: 18.32\n\nSummary table\n<table class=\"table\" style=\"width: auto !important; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th style=\"text-align:center;\"> parameter </th>\n   <th style=\"text-align:center;\"> mean </th>\n   <th style=\"text-align:center;\"> sd </th>\n   <th style=\"text-align:center;\"> q0.025 </th>\n   <th style=\"text-align:center;\"> q0.500 </th>\n   <th style=\"text-align:center;\"> q0.975 </th>\n   <th style=\"text-align:center;\"> ess </th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n<tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td style=\"text-align:center;\"> weights[1] </td>\n   <td style=\"text-align:center;\"> 0.997 </td>\n   <td style=\"text-align:center;\"> 0.013 </td>\n   <td style=\"text-align:center;\"> 0.95 </td>\n   <td style=\"text-align:center;\"> 1 </td>\n   <td style=\"text-align:center;\"> 1 </td>\n   <td style=\"text-align:center;\"> 116.315 </td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td style=\"text-align:center;\"> alpha </td>\n   <td style=\"text-align:center;\"> 0.353 </td>\n   <td style=\"text-align:center;\"> 0.24 </td>\n   <td style=\"text-align:center;\"> 0.086 </td>\n   <td style=\"text-align:center;\"> 0.29 </td>\n   <td style=\"text-align:center;\"> 1.018 </td>\n   <td style=\"text-align:center;\"> 114.006 </td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td style=\"text-align:center;\"> beta_scale[1, 1] </td>\n   <td style=\"text-align:center;\"> 0.172 </td>\n   <td style=\"text-align:center;\"> 0.182 </td>\n   <td